{"title": "Maps", "html": "<section class=\"l-section wpb_row us_custom_e11ab399 height_small\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_middle\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h2 class=\"w-post-elm post_title us_custom_47ffbcae align_center entry-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">Maps</h2><div class=\"w-separator size_small\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><!-- Row Backgrounds --><div class=\"upb_color\" data-bg-override=\"0\" data-bg-color=\"#eded9a\" data-fadeout=\"\" data-fadeout-percentage=\"30\" data-parallax-content=\"\" data-parallax-content-sense=\"30\" data-row-effect-mobile-disable=\"true\" data-img-parallax-mobile-disable=\"true\" data-rtl=\"false\"  data-custom-vc-row=\"\"  data-vc=\"6.1\"  data-is_old_vc=\"\"  data-theme-support=\"\"   data-overlay=\"false\" data-overlay-color=\"\" data-overlay-pattern=\"\" data-overlay-pattern-opacity=\"\" data-overlay-pattern-size=\"\"    ></div><section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_auto width_full\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-post-elm post_content\" itemprop=\"text\"><section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_medium\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h5>The National Water Resources Management Agency makes available national and individual river basin maps for viewing online. These maps were produced using the Free and Open Source Geographic Information System, QGIS. The GIS map data draws from and feeds back into the OpenStreetMap initiative. Topography is from the Shuttle Radar Topography Mission (SRTM). Details of our proposed national monitoring networks for rainfall, surface water and groundwater will be uploaded in the coming months.</h5>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"l-section wpb_row height_medium\"><div class=\"l-section-h i-cf\"><div class=\"g-cols vc_row type_default valign_top\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h6 class=\"font_4\">Please click on the images to enlarge them:</h6>\n</div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium with_line width_default thick_3 style_dotted color_secondary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><a class=\"w-image-h\" href=\"//assets/uploads/2020/02/map1.jpg\" ref=\"magnificPopup\"><img width=\"1979\" height=\"1249\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map1.jpg 1979w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map1-300x189.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map1-1024x646.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map1-1536x969.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1979px) 100vw, 1979px\" /></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-9 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h1>Map 1</h1>\n<h5>Sierra Leone’s river basins</h5>\n<p>This map shows Sierra Leone’s river basins, with their total areas and, in the case of trans-boundary basins, the areas that lie within Sierra Leone.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium with_line width_default thick_3 style_dotted color_secondary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><a class=\"w-image-h\" href=\"//assets/uploads/2020/02/map2-scaled.jpg\" ref=\"magnificPopup\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1665\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map2-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map2-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map2-300x195.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map2-1024x666.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map2-1536x999.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map2-2048x1332.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-9 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h1>Map 2</h1>\n<h5>Proposed River Monitoring Network</h5>\n<p>This map shows Sierra Leone’s river basins with the locations of proposed gauging stations to form a national river gauging network.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium with_line width_default thick_3 style_dotted color_secondary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><a class=\"w-image-h\" href=\"//assets/uploads/2020/02/map3-scaled.jpg\" ref=\"magnificPopup\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map3-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map3-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map3-300x195.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map3-1024x667.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map3-1536x1000.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map3-2048x1333.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-9 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h1>Map 3</h1>\n<h5>Proposed Meteorological Monitoring Network</h5>\n<p>This map shows Sierra Leone’s topographic relief and the locations of proposed meteorological stations comprising a national meteorological network.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium with_line width_default thick_3 style_dotted color_secondary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><a class=\"w-image-h\" href=\"//assets/uploads/2020/02/map4.jpg\" ref=\"magnificPopup\"><img width=\"1954\" height=\"1986\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map4.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map4.jpg 1954w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map4-295x300.jpg 295w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map4-1008x1024.jpg 1008w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map4-1511x1536.jpg 1511w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1954px) 100vw, 1954px\" /></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-9 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h1>Map 4</h1>\n<h5>Mean Annual Rainfall</h5>\n<p>This map shows the spatial distribution of rainfall over Sierra Leone, from two different published sources.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium with_line width_default thick_3 style_dotted color_secondary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><a class=\"w-image-h\" href=\"//assets/uploads/2020/02/map5-scaled.jpg\" ref=\"magnificPopup\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1663\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map5-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map5-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map5-300x195.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map5-1024x665.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map5-1536x998.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map5-2048x1330.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-9 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h1>Map 5</h1>\n<h5>Proposed Groundwater Monitoring network</h5>\n<p>This map shows a simplified geological map of Sierra Leone, with the locations of proposed groundwater monitoring points comprising a national groundwater monitoring network.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium with_line width_default thick_3 style_dotted color_secondary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><a class=\"w-image-h\" href=\"//assets/uploads/2020/02/map6-scaled.jpg\" ref=\"magnificPopup\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1660\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map6-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map6-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map6-300x195.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map6-1024x664.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map6-1536x996.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map6-2048x1328.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-9 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h1>Map 6</h1>\n<h5>Rokel-Seli Basin</h5>\n<p>This map shows the entire Rokel-Seli river basin.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium with_line width_default thick_3 style_dotted color_secondary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><a class=\"w-image-h\" href=\"//assets/uploads/2020/02/map7-scaled.jpg\" ref=\"magnificPopup\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1665\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map7-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map7-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map7-300x195.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map7-1024x666.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map7-1536x999.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map7-2048x1332.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-9 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h1>Map 7</h1>\n<h5>Rokel-Seli Basin Map A</h5>\n<p>This map shows the upper part of the Rokel-Seli river basin from the border with Guinea down almost to Bumbuna.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium with_line width_default thick_3 style_dotted color_secondary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><a class=\"w-image-h\" href=\"//assets/uploads/2020/02/map8-scaled.jpg\" ref=\"magnificPopup\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1664\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map8-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map8-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map8-300x195.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map8-1024x666.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map8-1536x998.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map8-2048x1331.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-9 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h1>Map 8</h1>\n<h5>Rokel-Seli Basin Map B</h5>\n<p>This map shows the middle part of the Rokel-Seli river basin from the Bumbuna dam and reservoir down as far as the Addax Estate.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium with_line width_default thick_3 style_dotted color_secondary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><a class=\"w-image-h\" href=\"//assets/uploads/2020/02/map9-scaled.jpg\" ref=\"magnificPopup\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1662\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map9-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map9-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map9-300x195.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map9-1024x665.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map9-1536x997.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map9-2048x1329.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-9 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h1>Map 9</h1>\n<h5>Rokel-Seli Basin Map C</h5>\n<p>This map shows the lower part of the Rokel-Seli river basin from Makeni – Magburaka to the Rokel estuary near Freetown.</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium with_line width_default thick_3 style_dotted color_secondary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div><div class=\"g-cols wpb_row  type_default valign_top vc_inner\"><div class=\"vc_col-sm-3 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"w-image align_center\"><a class=\"w-image-h\" href=\"//assets/uploads/2020/02/map10-scaled.jpg\" ref=\"magnificPopup\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1670\" src=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map10-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map10-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map10-300x196.jpg 300w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map10-1024x668.jpg 1024w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map10-1536x1002.jpg 1536w, https://nwrma.gov.sl//assets/uploads/2020/02/map10-2048x1336.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_col-sm-9 wpb_column vc_column_container\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h1>Map 10</h1>\n<h5>Rokel-Seli Pilot Area Sites</h5>\n<p>This map shows the locations of the monitoring points established by the Sierra Leone Water Security Project (mostly in the middle reach of the Rokel-Seli river basin).</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-separator size_medium with_line width_default thick_3 style_dotted color_secondary align_center\"><div class=\"w-separator-h\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></section>"}